&lt;p&gt;This role sits at the heart of DoorDash’s emergency response network — ensuring rapid, informed, and coordinated action during critical events such as natural disasters, workplace emergencies, or significant disruptions. Working closely with regional and global partners, you’ll help keep DoorDash’s people safe and operations running smoothly around the clock.&lt;/p&gt;
